    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2008-03-13</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2008-04-09T20:40:15Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Recapture Excess Profits and Invest in Roads and Rail (REPAIR) Act of 2008 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to impose in 2008 or 2009 an excise tax of 25% on the windfall profits of integrated oil companies and other producers and refiners of crude oil (crude oil condensates and natural gasoline) with gross receipts over $1 billion. </p><p>Allows a tax deduction for the payment of the windfall profit tax imposed by this Act. </p><p>Requires the transfer of windfall profit tax revenues to the Highway Trust Fund.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
